PrecisEnactment of the ENERGY EFFICIENCY REGULATIONS which establish national minimum energy efficiency performance standards for major household appliances, heating and cooling units or systems, water heaters, fluorescent lamp ballasts and electric motors, and require that an "EnerGuide" label disclosing their energy consumption be affixed to these goods.
